# I have successfully moved back to the stone furnace's location.
# 
# Now, I will insert the iron ore into the furnace to continue the smelting process. I should also ensure that the furnace has enough coal to operate.

insert_item(Prototype.IronOre, furnace, quantity=5)  # Inserting 5 iron ore into the furnace.
print(f"Furnace inventory: {inspect_inventory(furnace)}")  # Checking the furnace's inventory after the insertion.
